Saurin karuwa a cikin tarin cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin EU / EEA da UK daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Abubuwan da ke tattare da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) suna nuna irin wannan yanayin tsakanin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe, kodayake tana cikin matakai daban-daban dangane da ƙasa.
Bisa ga ilimin da aka samu daga Italiya, dole ne ƙasashe, asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da hankali su haɓaka shirye-shirye don saurin haɓaka marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kiwon lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa ta musamman.
An bayar da rahoton wani sabon kamuwa da cutar sankarar bargo da ba a san asalinsa ba a birnin Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin a ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ce an sanya sunan kwayar cutar coronavirus mai dauke da cutar mai dauke da cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin kwayar cutar da ke dauke da cutar.
Saboda haka, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Bayanai masu inganci a yau sun nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai laushi, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba kuma yawancin su sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu kamuwa da cutar, COVID-19 ya zama mafi muni wanda ke haifar da buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6% na masu kamuwa da cutar ke fuskantar rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke kwance a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken muna nazarin yanayin abubuwan da ke tattare da COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Ingila (UK) da kuma kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar a EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da UK
Kasar Sin ta biyo bayan COVID-19 da ke yaduwa a duniya, kuma halin da ake ciki a sauran sassan duniya a halin yanzu yana bin kasar.
Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon lamuran da aka tabbatar na Turai na COVID-19 bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta sanar da farko uku daga cikin mutane da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu kamuwa da COVID-19 a dukkan ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Ingila (UK), inda aka ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Ana samun adadi mai yawa na masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yaduwar su.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana da bayanai game da ƙididdigar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya da aka samo daga ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da kuma tushen hukuma kamar WHO, waɗanda aka sabunta kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da abin da ya faru a Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na barkewar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun kirga kwanaki 14 na gajeren lokaci na COVID-19, don haka muna la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 - 15 Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin adadin masu cutar da aka rubuta a kowace ƙasa har zuwa karfe 8:00 na safe ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu cutar a Italiya a cikin lokacin daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da UK
Yanayin karuwar kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya ya bi yanayin lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
Ga EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya gabaɗaya, ƙwayoyin cuta na COVID-19 sun fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan suka ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (ƙarin abu).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda saurin karuwar adadin masu cutar da aka ruwaito a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a cikin abubuwan da ke tattare da karuwar COVID-19 (kayan aiki).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna kwatancen lambobin Italiya da adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Ingila don lokacin 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya kamata a lura cewa, a karfe 8:00 na safe ranar 15 ga Maris, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar kamar Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin sanannun cututtukan COVID-19 suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya.
Yanayin da aka lura a cikin tarin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da saurin tafiya a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa kasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da bambance-bambance a cikin ma'anar masu yuwuwar kamuwa da cutar a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ladabi daban-daban don rarrabe marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kama-karya.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da hankali a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da asibiti da / ko shigar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a cikin sashin kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su ne kawai a cikin kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar a matakin EU / EEA (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Koyaya, ya kamata a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin adadin rahotannin da aka bayar da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a 2010/11 ya nuna bambanci mai yawa tsakanin wadatar gadaje masu kulawa da hankali da kuma matsakaiciyar kulawa a Turai, a cikin tsarin gadaje 4.2 a kowace 100,000 a Jamus daga 29.2 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙasa ko sama da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (gadoji 12.5 na kulawa mai tsanani da na tsaka-tsaki a cikin 100,000 a 201011).
Tare da yawan adadin COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti a kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya, yanayin samfurin da ke tattare da daidaitawar iyawar kiwon lafiya ya nuna cewa akwai haɗarin > 90% na wuce gona da iri na gadajen kulawa mai tsanani, kuma an bayar da shi a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC na COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment.
Tunda har yanzu akwai lamura a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da wasu yankuna na Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da raka'a na kulawa mai tsanani galibi suna ba da sabis na yanki ga jama'a, yana da kyau a sami bayanai game da masu cutar da gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin tsarin sanya sunan rukunin yanki don ƙididdigar 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Don haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da hankali su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da yaduwar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma yawan adadin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kiwon lafiya da kuma kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda ya faru a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimantawa na ECDC mai sauri, hanzari, mai saurin aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar da za a iya amfani da ita don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2 yana da mahimmanci, tare da sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da shi ba da wuri, saurin karuwar adadin lokuta ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da kuma daidaita martani ba.
Binciken hadarin gaggawa ya kuma bada jerin sunayen matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci na dama wanda ƙasashe za su iya ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba a yi hakan ba, akwai yiwuwar tsarin kiwon lafiya a wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa ko makonni.
