Kusan rabin wadanda suka kamu da cutar (47.7%) sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan sun kasance 'yan ƙasa da shekaru 20, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai ke fama da cutar da shekarunsu ba su kai 10 ba.
SARS-CoV-2 ya kamu da maza da yawa (0.27/100,000) fiye da mata (0.31/100,000).
COVID-19 ya bazu cikin sauri, musamman a Hubei da kewayenta.
