Manyan abubuwan haɗari guda uku na COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60) da kuma cutar huhu mai tsanani.
CoVs wani ƙaramin rukuni ne na ƙwayoyin cuta masu girma da yawa waɗanda ke ɗauke da ma'anar RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya raba su zuwa rukuni huɗu ko jinsi, wato, alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, daga cikinsu an san alpha da beta-CoVs suna cutar da mutane.
A cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, glycoprotein mai ɗauke da kebul (S) yana ɗaure da ƙwayoyin cuta masu karɓar kwayoyin halitta na angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) da dipeptideal peptidase 4 (DPP4), bi da bi, sannan kuma an haɗa su da membrane.
Kwayar RNA ta kwayar cutar ta saki a cikin kwayar halitta; bayan an kwafi kwayar cutar, envelope tare da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid sunadaran suna samar da kwayar RNA ta genomic tare da vesicles ko vesicles, wanda ya haɗu da membrane na plasma don saki kwayar cutar.
An ba da rahoton farkon yanayin kwayoyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
An gano cewa SARS-CoV-2 wani sabon nau'in beta-CoV ne wanda ke da asalin asalin asalin cutar tare da ganowar kwayoyin halitta sama da kashi 99.98% a cikin samfuran 10 da aka tattara daga kasuwar abincin teku ta Hunan a Wuhan.
A cikin kwayoyin halitta, SARS-CoV-2 yana da kamanceceniya da SARS-CoV fiye da MES-CoV.
Ta hanyar amfani da na'urar daukar hotan lantarki, an gano kwayoyin SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙananan sassan epithelium na numfashi na mutum.
An gano cewa mutum ACE2 ya kasance mai karɓar mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, sunadaran S na SARS-CoV-2 suna ɗaurewa ga ACE2 na ɗan adam da ƙarancin ƙarfi fiye da SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da ƙananan kamuwa da cuta a cikin marasa lafiya fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ya samar da ƙaramin ƙaramin furotin wanda aka ɓoye ta hanyar orf3b kuma yana iya samar da furotin wanda aka ɓoye ta hanyar orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 orf3b na iya taka rawa wajen haifar da cututtukan kwayar cuta da hana sakin IFNβ; duk da haka, orf8 ba shi da sanannen filin aiki ko tsari.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairun 2020, Zhou da sauransu sun ba da rahoton tsarin cryo-EM na cikakken tsayin ɗan adam ACE2 a cikin ma'auni mai ma'ana 2.9 Å a cikin kayan haɗin amino acid transporter B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa an haɗa mahaɗin da ke buɗe da rufewa a matsayin dimer, kuma mahaɗin ACE2-B0AT1 na iya ɗaure sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke ba da tabbaci ga ganewa da watsa CoV.
Don rage kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin warkewa don gwajin magunguna.
