A ranar 6 ga watan Maris, 2020, wasu masana ilimin annoba a kwalejin Imperial College London a Amurka sun ba da shawara game da tasirin da kuma tsinkayen sabon coronavirus a kasar.
A wannan ranar ne Shugaba Trump ya rattaba hannu kan Dokar Samun Kariyar Shirye-shiryen Kwayar cutar Coronavirus da Amsawa, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 na kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya don magance barkewar cutar.
Kamfanoni suna sanya takunkumi kan tafiye-tafiyen ma'aikata, soke taro da karfafa ma'aikata suyi aiki daga gida.
An soke wasanni da wasannin motsa jiki.A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanya dokar hana zirga-zirga na kwanaki 30 a yawancin Turai banda Burtaniya daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
A rana mai zuwa, ya kara fadada takunkumin zuwa ga Burtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta baci a duk fadin kasar, wanda hakan ya haifar da samar da kudaden tarayya don magance matsalar.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, yawancin kasuwancin Amurka sun rufe ko kuma sun rage lokacin aiki don rage saurin yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da cutar a cikin jihohi 50 da gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ba da rahoton cewa New York City tana da shari'o'in coronavirus 10,700, wanda ya fi yawan adadin masu cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, Gwamnan ya ce manufofin nisantar da jama'a suna aiki kamar yadda aka rage ƙididdigar ninki biyu daga 2.0 zuwa 4.7 a cikin kwanaki.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, New York City ta kai adadin kamuwa da cutar 32,308 da mutuwar mutane 672 daga cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, Amurka ta sami adadin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, gami da China da Italiya.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaban Amurka Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita umarnin nisantar da jama'a har zuwa ranar 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan rana, USNS Comfort, wani asibitin asibiti mai gadaje 1,000, ya kafa a New York.
A ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu, an samu mutuwar mutane 884 a Amurka a cikin sa'o'i 24 da suka gabata.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, cututtukan sun zarce mutane 100,000 a jihar New York. An soki Fadar White House saboda watsi da wannan alamar rashin jin daɗi da kuma sarrafa saƙon ta hanyar umarnin jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya don daidaita maganganun jama'a da wallafe-wallafe game da cutar a ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban Mike Pence.
An tabbatar da amincewar da Trump ya yi da tsarin rikicin da ya hada da jawabin jam'iyyar.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki dogaro da Amurka kan shigo da kayayyaki masu mahimmanci daga China, gami da kayan aikin likita masu mahimmanci.
An yi amfani da nazarin tsarin zirga-zirgar jiragen sama don tsarawa da kuma hango alamun yaduwar cututtuka kuma an buga shi a cikin The Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo da Taipei sun fi yawan matafiya daga Wuhan, bisa ga bayanan 2018 daga Transportungiyar Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Duniya.
Dubai, Sydney da Melbourne suma sun zama sanannun wuraren da masu yawon bude ido daga Wuhan suka ziyarta.
