A wannan rana, an ceto 'yan Kanada 215 (mutum 176 daga jirgin farko da 39 daga jirgin biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta ba da izini) daga Wuhan zuwa CFB Trenton kuma an kebe su na tsawon makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin saman Kanada mai fasinjoji 185 ya sauka a CFB Trenton daga Wuhan.
Hukumomin Australiya sun ceto 'yan ƙasa 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga Fabrairu kuma suka sanya su a Cibiyar Kula da Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka yi amfani da shi don sabon manufar matsayin wurin keɓewa, kuma sun kasance a can na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin sama na ƙaura daga New Zealand ya isa Auckland a ranar 5 ga Fabrairu; an killace fasinjojinsa (ciki har da wasu daga Australia da Pacific) a wani sansanin jiragen ruwa a Whangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe Amurkawa da ke cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess Proud.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin fasinja dauke da 'yan Kanada 129 ya tashi daga Diamond Princess zuwa Trenton, Ontario.
