An yi gwajin likita kafin tashi kuma an bar mutane hudu daga Afirka ta Kudu da ke nuna alamun cutar coronavirus don rage haɗarin.
Sai dai 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka yi gwajin cutar da ba su da lafiya, an sallame su.
Sakamakon gwajin ya tabbatar da cewa duk 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka shiga cikin ayyukan jin kai, ciki har da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, direbobi, ma'aikatan otal,' yan sanda da sojoji, ba su da wata damuwa kuma an killace sauran a cikin hutun ranch don kwanaki 14 a matsayin matakin kariya.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iran saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (da suka hada da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da tallafi ga kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin sun taru a Jami'ar Amurka don aika taimako zuwa wuraren da cutar ta addabi kasar Sin. Tare da su, wata kungiya daga yankin Chicago ta tura mashin N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a yankin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu. Kungiyar agajin jin kai ta hadin gwiwa tare da Direct Relief FedEx ta aika da mashin fuska 200,000 da sauran kayan kariya na sirri, gami da safar hannu, riguna zuwa asibitin Union na Wuhan a ranar 30 ga Janairu ta hanyar jirgin gaggawa.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken allurar rigakafi da kokarin magance cutar, tare da kare "mutane masu rauni a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Interaction ta bayyana cewa gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da gudummawar masks 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairu, bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya kai masks miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura tallafin da ya kai dala miliyan 2.26 ga kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan daya ga Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan aikin likita sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu na likitanci miliyan 18 ga China, Jamus ta ba da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya daban-daban, gami da kayan aikin hawan 10,000, kuma Amurka ta ba da tan 17.8 na kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin karin dala miliyan 100 na tallafin kudi ga kasashen da abin ya shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da masana don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance cutar coronavirus.
Dan kasuwa Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1 zuwa Addis Ababa, Habasha, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kayan kariya 60,000 don rarraba wa Tarayyar Afirka.
Daga baya ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin numfashi 5 zuwa Panama.
Ma kuma ta samar da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya a Kanada, ta nuna shakku kan abin da ake kira masks da kayan gwaji da aka yi daga Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Czech Republic.
Misali, Spain ta dawo da kayan gwajin coronavirus 58,000 da aka yi a China tare da ƙimar daidaito na 30% kawai, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da masks na fuska 600,000 na Sinawa, waɗanda ke da lahani.
Belgium ta dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, waɗanda aka ɗauka sun fito ne daga China, amma a zahiri sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, an yi maraba da manufofin kasar Sin a sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da jami'an kasar Sin ke yi na dakile da kuma kula da annobar.
WHO ta nuna bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS a 2002/2004 inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin sirri wanda ya kawo cikas ga kokarin hanawa da sarrafawa, da kuma rikicin yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ke ba da sabuntawa akai-akai don kauce wa fargaba kafin hutun sabuwar shekara ta Lunar.
"A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, wakilin WHO, Gordon Gally, ya yi sharhi game da shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na aiwatar da takunkumin hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan cewa ""WHO ba ta ba da shawarar hakan ba"", kuma wannan ""alamu ne masu mahimmanci na ƙaddamar da yunƙurin hana annobar duniya a inda ta fi yawa, inda ta fi yawaita", kuma ta kira shi ""ba a taɓa gani ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a"". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen China da kuma karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gagarumar matsalar lafiyar jama'a ta Duniya (Public Health Emergency of International Concern, PICHE), wanda shine karo na shida tun lokacin da WHO ta sanar da annobar duniya ta PICHE a lokacin annobar murar alade a shekarar 2009".
"Darakta Janar na WHO ya ce PHEIC ya faru ne saboda ""yanayin yaduwar duniya ya fi girma a ƙasashe masu karamin karfi da matsakaitan kuɗi waɗanda ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya".
"A cikin martani game da aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce ""babu wani dalili da zai sa a dauki matakan da za su tsoma baki ba tare da bukatar tafiya da kasuwanci ba"" kuma ya kara da cewa ""WHO ba ta bayar da shawarar takaita kasuwanci da motsi ba"."
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi al'ummar duniya da su bayar da tallafin dala miliyan 675 don shirye-shiryen dabaru a kasashe masu karamin karfi, tare da bayar da agajin gaggawa ga kasashen da ba su da wata hanyar sanin ko su waye ke da cutar a yankunansu, koda kuwa an kashe su.
"Tedros ya kuma bayyana cewa ""mu ne kamar yadda karfi kamar yadda mafi rauni source"" da kuma kira ga kasashen duniya ""don zuba jari a yau ko biya more daga baya"". WHO ya gabatar da sunan cutar a matsayin COVID-19 a wani taron manema labarai a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu".
"A ranar, Tedros ya sanar da cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da "ba da ƙarfin ga dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a matsayin martani".
"A sakamakon haka an kunna kungiyar kula da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita martani na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "mai da hankali kan martani na kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomin ke iya amfani da kwarewarsu don magance tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaban ci gaban cutar".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar WHO ta hada kai da kasar Sin don kawo kwararru na kasa da kasa da WHO zuwa kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen kula da gida da kuma tantance tsananin cutar da kuma iyawar ta ta hanyar bita da tarurruka tare da manyan hukumomin kasa da kasa da kuma tafiya zuwa wurare masu dacewa don tantance tasirin da kuma martani ga ayyukan a matakin lardi da na lardi, gami da birane da yankuna.A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta sanar da cewa duniya tana shirin kara shirya don wannan annobar cutar coronavirus, inda ta ce duk da cewa ba a ayyana ta a matsayin annoba ba, ya kamata a kasance a matakin shirye-shirye na kasashe.
"A sakamakon karuwar barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta tura wani hadin gwiwa don tantance halin da ake ciki a can. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana a hukumance cewa za a kara darajar hadarin coronavirus a duniya daga ""mai girma"" zuwa ""mai matukar girma"", wanda shine matakin da ya fi dacewa da faɗakarwa da kimantawa".
"Darakta na zartarwa na shirin gaggawa na lafiya na WHO Mike Ryan ya yi gargadin a cikin wata sanarwa cewa ""wannan gwaji ne na gaske ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: farkawa".
"Wannan kwayar cutar na iya kasancewa a kusa kuma dole ne ku kasance cikin shiri", "Magana mai kyau na iya taimakawa duniya kauce wa mafi munin yanayin".
"Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa bayanan da ake da su yanzu ba su ba da hujjojin da jami'an kiwon lafiya ke bukata don ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ba, kuma ya ce irin wannan sanarwar na nufin ""Mun yarda cewa kowa a duniya zai kamu da cutar""".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris ne WHO ta ayyana cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
"Darakta mai gudanarwa ya ce WHO tana da matukar damuwa game da "damuwa game da yaduwar cutar da kuma rashin lafiyarta. WHO ta fuskanci zargi mai yawa saboda rashin kula da cutar, gami da jinkirin ayyana gaggawa na lafiyar jama'a da kuma jinkirin rarraba kwayar cutar a matsayin annoba".
Sakamakon rashin jin daɗi ya haɗa da takarda mai neman murabus daga Darakta-Janar na WHO, Tedros Adhanom, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, wasu masana kan kare hakkin bil adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun yi bayani kan girmama hakkin kowa a lokacin COVID-19.
Kungiyar kwararru ta ce kowa na da hakkin yin ayyukan ceto rayuka kuma gwamnati ce ke da alhakin hakan.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa rashin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya ba zai taba zama hujja ba don nuna bambanci ga wasu kungiyoyi.
Masana sun jaddada cewa nakasassu, 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, marasa gida, marasa gida, wadanda ke rayuwa cikin talauci, wadanda ke cikin kurkuku, 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ba a kula da su ba wadanda ke bukatar taimakon gwamnati, duk suna da hakkin samun lafiya.
Hukumomin gwamnati na duniya suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwa kan tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kafa wani dandali don samar da bayanai masu dacewa da kuma cikakkun bayanai kan martani na manufofi a kasashe a duniya, tare da samar da hangen nesa da shawarwari.
Tattalin Arzikin Duniya ya ƙunshi bin diddigin manufofin ƙasa don magance tasirin ƙaura daga ƙa'idodin ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya zuwa tafiye-tafiye, ƙuntatawa na cibiyar dijital da kulle kulle, kuma yana da nufin taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da sauƙaƙe haɗin kai a duniya don amsa ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Gwamnatin Amurka, Ministan Ofishin Ministocin Burtaniya Michael Gove da dan Shugaba Jair Bolsonaro na Brazil, Eduardo Bolsonaro, sun soki gwamnatin China kan yadda ta magance cutar, wacce ta fara ne a yankin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori wasu jami'an kwaminisanci na kasar Sin (CPC) da dama daga aiki saboda kokarin da suka yi na killace mutane a yankin tsakiyar kasar Sin, wanda hakan ya nuna rashin jin dadin kungiyoyin siyasa da ke mayar da hankali kan barkewar cutar a wadannan yankuna.
