"Gwamnatin Donald Trump ta Amurka ta kira coronavirus da ""Cinema ta Sin"" ko ""Cutar Wuhan"" ta ce, "Yanayin da China ke ciki na sanya cutar ta zama babbar cuta a duniya", wanda wasu masu sukar suka yi ta sukar wariyar launin fata da kuma "kokarin karkatar da hankali daga gazawar gwamnatin ta wajen dakile cutar".
"The Daily Beast ta yi magana game da yadda gwamnatin Amurka ke gudanar da ayyukanta, ta bayyana dabarun sadarwa tare da majiyoyi masu tushe a Majalisar Tsaro ta Kasa, inda aka ambaci dabarun a matsayin ""duk game da China".
"An umarce mu da mu yi kokarin yada wannan sakon ta duk wata hanya da za mu iya, ciki har da taron manema labarai da kuma nunawa a talabijin. ""Kasuwanci kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin da China ke yi na tura tallafi ga kasashen da ke fama da cutar na daga cikin yakin neman tasirin duniya".
"Joseph Borel, shugaban harkokin wajen Tarayyar Turai, ya yi gargadin cewa akwai wani bangare na siyasa da ya hada da "kirkirar labarai da kuma gwagwarmayar samun tasiri ta hanyar 'siyasa ta sassaucin ra'ayi'".
"Borrell ya kara da cewa, ""China tana nuna karfi wajen tura sakon cewa, sabanin Amurka, ita abokiyar zama ce mai dogaro da dogaro da ita"."
China ta nemi Amurka ta dakatar da bayar da tallafi ga kasashen Syria, Venezuela da Iran, bayan da aka samu rahotanni cewa ita kanta tana aikawa da tallafi ga wadannan kasashen biyu.
