"Dimitry Peskov, mai magana da yawun Kremlin ya ce, ""Idan ya zo ga taimaka wa abokan aikinsa na Amurka, [Putin] yana tunanin cewa idan masana'antun kayan aikin likitancin Amurka suka sami wasu matakai, za su iya ba da gudummawa"."
"An shirya atisayen sojin NATO ""Defender 2020"" a Jamus, Poland da Baltic, wanda shine mafi girman atisayen NATO tun bayan ƙarshen Cold War, za a yi su a cikin ƙananan girma".
"Sakataren Janar na Kamfen na Yaki da Makaman Nukiliya Kate Hudson ya soki atisayen Defender 2020: ""A cikin rikicin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na yanzu, ba wai kawai zai yi barazanar rayuwar sojojin Amurka da sauran kasashen Turai da ke halartar ba, har ma da rayukan mazauna kasashen da suke iko da su. "" Gwamnatin Iran ta yi fama da cutar sosai, tare da wasu 'yan majalisa biyu da suka kamu da cutar da kuma wasu manyan jami'ai goma sha biyu da ke aiki a yanzu ko kuma tsoffin jami'ai".
Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wata wasika a ranar 14 ga watan Maris, 2020 ga shugabannin duniya don neman taimako, inda ya ce takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya wa Iran yana sanya musu wahala wajen yaki da barkewar cutar saboda kasarsa ba ta da damar shiga kasuwannin duniya.
