Kula da haɗarin wurin aiki don COVID-19
Kula da haɗarin aiki don COVID-19 shine aiwatar da ayyukan lafiya da kiwon lafiya na sana'a don sarrafa haɗarin don hana cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ingantattun matakan haɗarin aiki sun dogara da wurin aiki da aikin da ake yi, kimanta haɗarin hanyoyin haɗuwa, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan haɗarin ma'aikata na mutum waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da COVID-19.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Aikin Aiki ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙananan haɗarin haɗuwa suna ƙarancin hulɗa da jama'a da sauran abokan aiki, wanda ke ba da shawarar matakan hana kamuwa da cuta, gami da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, ladabi na numfashi, da tsaftacewa da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki a kai a kai.
Ayyukan haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da ayyukan da ba a san ko ake zargin cewa suna da COVID-19 ba, amma suna buƙatar haɗuwa ko kusanci da mutane da ke iya kamuwa da cutar saboda cutar da ke yaduwa a cikin al'umma a wuraren aiki ko ta hanyar balaguron ƙasa da ƙasa.
Wannan ya hada da ma'aikatan da ke hulɗa da jama'a, kamar a makarantu, wuraren aiki masu yawan jama'a, da kuma wasu wuraren sayar da kayayyaki masu cunkoso.
Baya ga matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta na farko, matakan kula da haɗari ga wannan rukunin sun haɗa da samun iska ta hanyar amfani da matattarar iska mai ƙarfi, masu tsaron kankara da kayan kariya na mutum idan sun haɗu da mutumin da ke da cutar COVID-19.
OSHA ta yi imanin cewa ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da masu aiki a dakin gawa suna da haɗarin haɗuwa da mutanen da ke da tabbacin ko kuma waɗanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19.
Kula da haɗarin da ya dace ga waɗannan ma'aikatan ya haɗa da sarrafa injiniyoyi kamar ɗakunan iska mai matsin lamba, da kayan kariya na sirri da suka dace da aikin.
Cutar COVID-19 na iya haifar da tasiri da yawa a wuraren aiki.
Ma'aikata na iya yin rashin aiki saboda rashin lafiya, kula da wasu, ko tsoron yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Kasuwanci na iya canzawa ta hanyoyi biyu, wanda shine abin da ake buƙata da kuma yadda ake sayen waɗannan kayayyaki (kamar yin sayayya a lokacin da ba aiki ko ta hanyar bayarwa ko sabis na tuki).
A ƙarshe, jigilar kaya daga yankunan da COVID-19 ya shafa sosai na iya zama cikas. Za a iya amfani da shirye-shiryen cututtukan cututtuka da shirin amsawa don ba da umarnin matakan kariya.
Shirye-shiryen suna magance matakan haɗari da ke tattare da wurare daban-daban da ayyukan da ake yi, gami da tushen haɗari, abubuwan haɗari da ke fitowa daga gida da zamantakewar jama'a, da abubuwan haɗari na mutum ga ma'aikata kamar tsufa ko yanayin rashin lafiya mai tsawo.
Sun kuma bayyana matakan da ake bukata don magance wadannan kasada da kuma shirin da za a yi na shirya wa yanayin da zai iya tasowa sakamakon barkewar cutar.
Shirye-shiryen shirye-shiryen cututtuka da shirye-shiryen amsawa na iya zama batun shawarwari na ƙasa ko na ƙasa.
Manufofin mayar da martani ga barkewar cutar sun hada da rage kamuwa da cuta tsakanin ma'aikata, kare mutanen da ke cikin hadarin kamuwa da cututtukan kiwon lafiya, ci gaba da ayyukan kasuwanci da rage tasirin tasirin tasirin su ga sauran kamfanoni a cikin sarkar samar da su.
Matsayin cutar a cikin al'ummomin da kasuwancin yake yana shafar yadda ake amsawa.
Tsarin tsari na kula da haɗari shine tsarin da aka yi amfani dashi don sarrafa ayyukan lafiya da lafiya.
Inda ba za a iya kawar da haɗarin COVID-19 ba, mafi ingantattun matakan sarrafawa sune sarrafa injiniya, sannan sarrafawa, kuma a ƙarshe kayan kariya na mutum.
Injiniyan sarrafawa ya ƙunshi ware ma'aikata daga haɗarin aiki ba tare da dogaro da halayen ma'aikata ba, kuma yana iya zama mafita mafi arha don aiwatarwa.
Gudanarwa na gudanarwa shine canji a cikin manufofi ko hanyoyin aiki wanda ke buƙatar aiki daga ma'aikaci ko mai aiki.
Kayan aikin kare kai (PPE) ana ɗaukarsu marasa tasiri fiye da na injiniya da ƙa'idodin gudanarwa, amma suna iya taimakawa hana wasu fallasa.
Dole ne ma'aikaci ya zaɓi duk nau'ikan PPE bisa haɗarin, ya dace da dacewa kamar yadda ya dace (kamar masu numfashi), ya kasance mai daidaituwa da dacewa, bincika, kulawa da maye gurbin su akai-akai, kuma ya buɗe, tsabtace, kuma adana ko zubar da su yadda ya kamata don kauce wa gurɓataccen abu.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Aikin Aiki ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙananan haɗarin haɗuwa suna da iyakantaccen hulɗa da jama'a da sauran abokan aiki.
Matakan farko na rigakafin kamuwa da cuta da aka ba da shawarar ga dukkan wuraren aiki sun haɗa da wanke hannu da kyau da kyau, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida idan suna rashin lafiya, ba da ladabi na numfashi, gami da rufe fuska yayin hancin da tari, samar da kayan shafawa da kayan shara, shirya don sadarwa idan ya cancanta ko sauye sauye a rana, hana ma'aikata amfani da kayan aiki da kayan aiki na wasu, da kuma kiyaye al'ada don tsabtace da kuma tsabtace yanayin aiki.
Ganowa da kuma ware mutanen da ke da cutar da wuri yana da mahimmanci don kiyaye ma'aikata, abokan ciniki, masu neman aiki da sauransu cikin aminci a wuraren aiki.
Ma'aikata da ke da alamun rashin lafiya mai tsanani na numfashi sun ba da shawarar cewa Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar su zauna a gida, har sai sun sami ƙarancin zazzabi, alamun zazzabi, da sauran alamun cutar na aƙalla awanni 24 ba tare da amfani da maganin rage zazzabi ko wasu magungunan da ke canza alamun cutar ba, kuma ya kamata a sassauta manufofin hutu na rashin lafiya, wanda zai ba ma'aikaci damar zama a gida don kula da dangin da ke rashin lafiya, kuma ya kamata ma'aikata su san waɗannan manufofin.
A cewar OSHA, ayyukan haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da ayyukan da ba a san ko ake zargin cewa suna da COVID-19 ba, amma suna buƙatar haɗuwa ko kusanci da mutane sau da yawa tsakanin ƙafa shida (1.8 m) waɗanda ƙila sun kamu da SARS-CoV-2 saboda cutar da ke gudana a cikin jama'a a wurin aiki ko kuma kwanan nan tafiya ta ƙasa da ƙasa zuwa wani wuri inda mutumin ya sami yaduwar COVID-19.
Waɗannan sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke da hulɗa da jama'a, kamar a makarantu, a cikin yanayin aiki mai haɗari, da kuma a cikin wasu shaguna masu yawan jama'a. Don haka, da kuma don ƙungiyoyin haɗari masu haɗari, sarrafawa na injiniya sun haɗa da sanya matattarar iska mai ƙarfi, haɓaka ƙimar iska, sanya shinge na jiki kamar masu tsabtace filastik, da kuma kafa taga mai ƙarfi don sabis na abokin ciniki. Don haka, da kuma don ƙungiyoyin haɗari masu haɗari, ana buƙatar kula da gudanarwa don ƙarfafa ma'aikata su kasance a gida ko a wuraren aiki marasa lafiya, samar da damar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa ta hanyar haɗuwa, gabatar da horo game da yadda za a iya daidaitawa da ma'aikata (staggered), amfani da kayan aikin da keɓaɓɓun kayan aiki a cikin gidajen da ba su da haɗari ga COVID-19 don hana abokan ciniki yin tafiya da hannu da hannu, samar da takamaiman bayanai game da yanayin aiki, samar da takamaiman hanyoyin kula da lafiya, da kuma yin amfani da kayan aikin da keɓaɓɓu, da kuma samar da hanyoyin sadarwa masu dacewa da ke nuna haɗari ga COVID-19, da kuma samar da takamaiman bayanai game da yanayin aiki, da kuma yadda za a kiyaye lafiyar jiki da kuma kiyaye kariya, da kuma kiyaye wasu abubuwan da suka shafi haɗari.
Ma'aikata a cikin wannan rukunin haɗarin suna buƙatar yin amfani da injin numfashi a cikin ƙananan lokuta.
Idan wani ya kamu da rashin lafiya a cikin jirgin sama, matakan da suka dace don kare ma'aikata da sauran fasinjoji sun haɗa da nisantar da mara lafiya daga wasu a tazarar ƙafa 6, sanya wani ma'aikaci don kula da mara lafiya, da samar da abin rufe fuska ga mara lafiya ko tambayar mara lafiya ya rufe baki da hanci da nama yayin yin fitsari ko tari.
Ya kamata ma'aikatan jirgin su sanya safar hannu ta likita mai yarwa yayin amsa kiran matafiyi mara lafiya ko taɓa ruwa na jiki ko yiwuwar gurɓataccen farfajiyoyi, kuma wataƙila su yi amfani da ƙarin kayan kariya na sirri idan matafiyin mara lafiya yana da zazzabi, tari mai ɗorewa ko numfashi.
Ya kamata a zubar da safofin hannu da sauran abubuwan da za a iya zubar da su a cikin jakar haɗarin haɗari, kuma a tsabtace da kuma kashe ƙwayoyin cuta a bayan haka. Ga jiragen ruwa na kasuwanci, ciki har da jiragen ruwa da sauran jiragen ruwa masu fasinja, kulawar haɗari sun haɗa da jinkirta tafiya idan suna rashin lafiya, ware kansu, da sanar da cibiyar kiwon lafiya ta jirgin nan da nan idan wani ya kamu da zazzabi ko wasu alamomi yayin da suke cikin jirgin.
A cikin yanayin da ya dace, ya kamata a bi diddigin likita a cikin ɗakin da aka keɓe. A cikin makarantu da wuraren kula da yara, CDC ta ba da shawarar rufewa na ɗan lokaci don tsaftacewa ko kashe ƙwayoyin cuta idan wani mai cutar ya shiga ginin makaranta, ba tare da la'akari da yaduwar cutar a cikin jama'a ba.
Lokacin da cutar ta kasance a cikin ƙananan matsakaici a cikin al'umma, ana iya aiwatar da dabarun nisantar da jama'a, kamar soke tafiye-tafiye, tarurruka da sauran manyan tarurruka, kamar karatun jiki ko cin abinci a cikin azuzuwan kiɗa ko cafeterias; ƙara nesa tsakanin tebur, raba lokutan zuwa ofis da hutu, iyakance ganawa da ba dole ba, da amfani da sararin ofis na kiwon lafiya daban don yara masu alamun mura.
Idan akwai cutar a cikin al'ummomin gida, ana iya yin la'akari da ƙara yawan lokacin hutu na makaranta don ƙarin dabarun nisantar da jama'a.
Jami'an tilasta yin doka da ke da alaƙa da mutanen da ke da tabbacin ko ana zargin suna da COVID-19 an shawarce su da su bi ƙa'idodin da masu aikin gaggawa ke bi, gami da kayan kariya na sirri.
Idan ma'aikata sun kusanci a lokacin haɗari, dole ne a tsabtace da kuma kashe ƙwayoyin cuta tare da amfani da fesa tsabtace gida ko gogewa kafin sake amfani da belin aiki da kayan aiki, kuma a bi hanyoyin gudanar da hujja don sarrafawa da kuma kawar da PPE da aka yi amfani da su.
OSHA ta ɗauki wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da na mutuwa a matsayin masu haɗarin haɗari ko haɗari.
Ayyukan haɗari masu haɗari sun haɗa da masu ba da kiwon lafiya, masu ba da taimako, ma'aikatan dakin gwaje-gwaje, da ma'aikatan jigilar kayayyaki waɗanda ke haɗuwa da marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargi da COVID-19.
Idan ma'aikata suna yin hanyoyin samar da aerosol, ko tattara ko motsa samfura daga marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargi da COVID-19, waɗannan suna da haɗarin haɗuwa.
Hanyoyin samar da aerosol sun hada da shigar da bututu, hanyoyin fara tari, bronchoscopy, wasu hanyoyin hakori da kuma tattara samfuran ta hanyar shigar da gwaji ko kayan aiki.
Ayyukan haɗari masu haɗari, da ke da alaƙa da mutuwa sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke cikin aikin shirya gawawwakin duk mutanen da aka sani ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwar; wannan ya zama haɗari mai haɗari sosai idan sun yi bincike. Ƙarin ƙwarewar injiniya ga mutanen da ke cikin wannan rukunin haɗari sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19, gami da lokacin da ake aiwatar da hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
Hanyoyin iska masu ƙarancin ƙarfi na musamman na iya zama masu dacewa da wasu wuraren kiwon lafiya da kuma yanayin gidan gawa.
Ya kamata a sarrafa samfurori bisa ga matakan tsaro na 3.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa masu zuwa marasa lafiya su keɓe su zuwa wuraren jira daban-daban dangane da ko ana zargin suna da COVID-19. OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu numfashi ban da sauran PPE ga mutanen da ke aiki a cikin ƙafa 6 na waɗanda aka sani ko ake zargin suna da SARS-CoV-2 da kuma mutanen da ke yin hanyoyin samar da aerosol.
A cikin Amurka, dole ne a yi amfani da N95 ko mafi kyawun tacewar fuska a cikin mahallin cikakken, rubutaccen shirin kariya na numfashi, gami da gwajin lafiya, horo da gwaji na likita.
Sauran nau'ikan na'urorin numfashi na iya samar da ƙarin kariya da haɓaka jin daɗin ma'aikaci. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar rufewa ba, saboda COVID-19 ba ya yaduwa ta hanyar abubuwan ruwa na jiki, amma cutar numfashi ce.
WHO ta ba da shawarar rufe fuska na tiyata ga ma'aikatan da ke yin gwajin a ƙofar shiga kawai.
WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da abin rufe fuska, tabarau, ko garkuwar fuska, riguna da safar hannu ga waɗanda ke tattara, kula da, ko jigilar samfurori na numfashi daga marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da wata hanyar samar da aerosol ba.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, ana maye gurbin abin rufe fuska da N95 ko FFP2 respirator.
Ganin rashin isasshen kayan PPE a duniya, WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da telemedicine, amfani da tazara ta jiki kamar windows mai haske don rage buƙatun PPE, da barin waɗanda ke da alaƙa da kulawa kai tsaye su shiga ɗakunan da ke da mai cutar COVID-19 ɗaya, amfani da PPE kawai don takamaiman aiki, ci gaba da amfani da shi ba tare da cire na'urar numfashi ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa da cutar iri ɗaya, ba da izinin saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da kuma hana masu rashin alamun sanya abin rufe fuska.
