BAngiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani mai haɓaka ne wanda ke haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da ƙwayoyin cuta (ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta).
ACE2 yana hana aikin aikin enzymes masu canzawa na angiotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da kuma kara Ang ((1-7) wanda ya sa ya zama kyakkyawan maƙasudin magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin wuri don shiga cikin sel don wasu coronaviruses.
An kira kwayar halitta ta mutum na enzyme hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani zinc-mai karɓar metallolenzymes ne wanda ke zaune a kan endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin halitta.
ACE2 yana da wani nau'i na N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma wani nau'i na C-terminal colectin na renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 shine nau'in membrane mai nau'in nau'i na I wanda yake da ƙwayar cuta wanda ke nuna alamar ƙwayar cuta a cikin huhu da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Ana rarraba yankin waje na ACE2 daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira shades kuma sakamakon furotin mai narkewa yana sakin jini kuma a ƙarshe ya fita ta fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗuwa da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na alveoli na nau'in II na huhu, da ƙananan ƙwayoyin hanji, da ƙwayoyin arterial da endothelial na yawancin gabobin jiki, da ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin tsoka na arteries.
Ana kuma samun bayanin mRNA na ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, stratum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine aiki a matsayin mai daidaitawa na ACE.
ACE yana raba hormone na angiotensin I zuwa vasokonstricting angiotensin II.
ACE2 ya ware carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) daga angiotensin II kuma ya hada shi da hydrolyzed zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya rarrabe wasu peptides, ciki har da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A da ghrelin.
ACE2 yana sarrafa musayar membrane na SLC6A19, mai jigilar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki kuma yana da alaƙa da cututtukan zuciya.
ACE2 a matsayin furotin mai canzawa yana aiki a matsayin babban hanyar shiga cikin kwayar halitta don wasu coronaviruses, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (wanda ke da alhakin SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke da alhakin COVID-19).
Musamman, SARS-CoV da kuma spike S1 sun haɗa da sunadarai a cikin ƙwayar enzymatic na ACE2 zuwa farfajiyar tantanin halitta wanda ke haifar da endocytosis da kuma maye gurbin ƙwayoyin cuta da enzymes zuwa cikin ƙwayoyin halitta.
Wannan tsarin shigarwa yana buƙatar maida hankali kan furotin S ta hanyar mai karɓar serine protease TMPRSS2, wanda hana shi a halin yanzu ana bincika shi azaman mai warkarwa. Wannan ya taimaka wa wasu suyi tunanin cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin sel na iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
