A cikin mutane, rabin rayuwar rhACE2 kusan awanni 10 ne kuma farawa aiki a cikin mintuna 30, kuma tsawon lokacin tasiri (tsayawa) shine awanni 24.
Abubuwan da aka gano sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama mai kyau ga mutanen da ba za su iya jure wa masu hana tsarin renin-angiotensin na farko ba (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma waɗanda ke da cututtuka inda haɓakar angiotensin II ta karu. An kimanta rhACE2 a cikin gwajin gwaji don bayyanar cututtuka na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (acute respiratory distress syndrome).
