b'A allurar rigakafin COVID-19 allurar rigakafi ce da aka tsara don cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19).
Ko da yake babu wani allurar rigakafi da ya kammala gwajin gwaji, akwai ƙoƙari da yawa da ke ci gaba don samar da irin wannan allurar.
A ƙarshen Fabrairun 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ce ba ta tsammanin za a sami allurar rigakafin cutar SARS-CoV-2 mai aiki a cikin ƙasa da watanni 18.
A watan Afrilu, akwai 'yan takarar allurar rigakafi biyar a cikin gwajin aminci na farko.
An gano COVID-19 a watan Disamba na 2019.
A shekarar 2020 wani babban barkewar cutar ya barke a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da zuba jari da kuma gudanar da bincike mai yawa don samar da allurar rigakafi.
Yawancin kamfanoni suna amfani da kwayoyin halittar da aka saki don haɓaka alluran rigakafi masu yuwuwa akan SARS-CoV-2.
A watan Afrilu, an ce, abubuwan da ke buƙatar CEPI don samar da allurar rigakafi sune saurin, ƙarfin samarwa, aikace-aikace da yawa da samun damar duniya.
A watan Afrilu, masana kimiyya na CEPI sun ba da rahoton cewa a farkon 2020 akwai dandamali daban-daban na fasaha 10 da ke aiki don Bincike da Ci gaban don ƙirƙirar allurar rigakafi mai tasiri akan COVID-19.
Babban manufofin dandamali da suka ci gaba a cikin karatun tsaro na Phase I sun hada da:
Kwayoyin nucleic (DNA da RNA) (Mataki na I mai haɓakawa da mai neman allurar rigakafi: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Mai ɗaukar hoto mai ɗaukar hoto (Mataki na I mai haɓakawa da mai neman allurar rigakafi: Cancino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Kamar yadda masana kimiyya na CEPI suka bayyana a watan Afrilu, jimillar mutane 115 da aka yi wa allurar rigakafi suna cikin matakan farko na ci gaba, daga cikinsu 78 an tabbatar da su a matsayin ayyukan aiki (79 a cewar Cibiyar Milken) da kuma 37 da aka ruwaito a matsayin wasu, amma duk sun fito ne daga bayanan da ba a bayyana su ga jama'a ba (wanda ake tsammani ana shirin).
Gwajin Phase I-II yana gudanar da gwajin farko na aminci da rigakafi kuma ana yin sa ne a wurare da yawa, ana sarrafa su da wuribo, yayin da ake ƙaddamar da takamaiman, ingantattun allurai.
Gwaje-gwaje na kashi na uku, tare da gwajin ingancin allurar rigakafi don hana cututtuka da rukunin kulawa, yawanci suna ɗaukar mahalarta da yawa, yayin da ake lura da tasirin sakamako mara kyau a cikin mafi kyawun sashi.
"Daga cikin 'yan takarar allurar rigakafi 79 da ke cikin ci gaba (kamar yadda aka tabbatar a farkon Afrilu 2020), 74 ba a tantance su a cikin ɗan adam ba tukuna (har yanzu suna ƙarƙashin binciken ""preclinical"")".
