Sun so su samar da allurar rigakafin da za a iya gwadawa a cikin mutane cikin kwanaki 90.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, 2020, Jami'ar Washington a St. Louis ta sanar da shirye-shiryen samar da allurar rigakafi.
A ranar 5 ga Maris, 2020, Sojojin Amurka na Bincike da Kayan Aiki a Fort Detrick da Walter Reed Army Institute of Research a Silver Spring, duka biyu a yammacin Maryland, sun ba da sanarwar cewa suna aiki kan allurar rigakafi.
A ranar 10 ga Maris, 2020, Emergent Biosolutions ta sanar da cewa ta haɗu da Novavax Inc.
